lor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714747" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="43"><SIZE Height="1875" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5310" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>lim _{K-&gt; 0} {f  _{K} = INF }</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="51" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714748" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="44"><SIZE Height="1875" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5310" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>lim _{K-&gt; 0} {f  _{K} = INF }</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="27" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><CHAR>ⅱ) 자본은 가역적(</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>reversible)</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="30"><CHAR>이다. 즉, 자본은 감소할 수 있다.</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="5" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="33"><AUTONUM Number="30" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 보조적인 가정으로서 자본은 항상 완전히 사용된다고 가정. 즉 한 시점에서 자본의 활용률은 1이다. 경기가 안 좋을 때 공장의 80%만 활용하는 것이 아니라 공장이 기존의 80%로 축소되서 활용은 100% 된다. 자본이 가분성을 갖고 있어 분수로 표시될 수 있다. </CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="34" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="34" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><CHAR>K(t), I(t) ≶ 0  </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="34" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="27" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><CHAR>ⅲ) 신규투자는 자본의 변동분과 상각되서 없어지는 분량을 합한 것</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="32" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714749" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="111"><SIZE Height="2250" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="8240" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>I(t)= {dK} over {dt} + delta K(t)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> , </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714750" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="112"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="450" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>delta </SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ; 상각률(시간에 상관없이 일정)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="32" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="35" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><CHAR>ⅳ) 노동과 투자는 각각의 가격에 영향을 미치지 않는다. 요소시장이 완전경쟁적이므로 임금과 자본 가격은 주어진 것으로 가정</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="35" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="31" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714751" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="109"><SIZE Height="2250" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3335" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{dL} over {dw} =0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ,  </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714752" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="110"><SIZE Height="2250" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3410" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{dK} over {d rho } =0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>  </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="31" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="27" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="1"><CHAR>&lt;모형&gt;</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><CHAR>기업은 총수입에서 투입요소비용을 뺀 순현금흐름(net cash flow)의 현재가치를 최대화하는 것이 목적이다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><EQUATION BaseLine="62" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714753" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="20"><SIZE Height="2586" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="16673" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>it max``````  int _{0} ^{INF } {e  ^{-rt}} [pf(L,K)-wL- rho I]dt</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714754" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="21"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7950" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>s.t`````````````K prime =I- delta K</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><CHAR>p(t) ; t 시점에서 생산물 가격</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><CHAR>r(t)=r ; 이자율 또는 투자수익률(시간에 상관없이 일정)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><CHAR>(풀이)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><CHAR>상태변수는 K(t), 통제변수는 L(t), I(t)</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="5" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="33"><AUTONUM Number="31" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 목적범함수에는 표기의 편의상 각 변수가 시간 t의 함수임을 생략했다.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><CHAR>Hamiltonian 함수는</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><EQUATION BaseLine="89" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714755" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="22"><SIZE Height="1163" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="18508" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>H=e  ^{-rt} [pf(L,K)-wL- rho I]+ lambda (I- delta K)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><CHAR>ⓐ 통제변수 L 최적화 조건</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714756" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="23"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10538" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>H  _{L} =e  ^{