 VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>=- {U prime (f prime -( theta +r))} over {U '' }</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><CHAR>충분조건:</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><CHAR>효용함수가 오목함수이고 효용함수의 가정에 의해 충분조건을 만족한다.</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="5" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="33"><AUTONUM Number="37" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 또한 내부해를 갖는다고 가정</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><CHAR>최적해의 필요조건</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><TABLE BorderFill="3" CellSpacing="0" ColCount="1" PageBreak="Cell" RepeatHeader="true" RowCount="1"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714839" Lock="false" NumberingType="Table" ZOrder="154"><SIZE Height="6864" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="19882" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Column" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="283" Left="283" Right="283" Top="283"/></SHAPEOBJECT><INSIDEMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><ROW><CELL BorderFill="4" ColAddr="0" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="6864" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="19882"><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714840" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="155"><SIZE Height="2250" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="11365" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>c'(t)=- {U prime (f prime -( theta +r))} over {U '' }</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ; 최적화조건</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714841" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="156"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7795" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>k'=f(k)- theta k-c</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ; 경제성장기본식</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW></TABLE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><CHAR>위 두 미분방정식을 만족시키는 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714842" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="152"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5300" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" Hor