rtAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>c'(t)= {U prime (f prime -( theta +r))} over {U '' } =0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ⇒ </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714845" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="161"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6165" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f prime (k*)= theta +r</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><CHAR>경제성장기본식에서</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714846" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="172"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10955" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>k'(t)=f(k)- theta k-c`=0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ⇒ </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714847" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="173"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7425" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(k*)- theta k*=c`*</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><CHAR>앞의 Solow-Swan 모형에서 황금률 경제성장경로는 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714848" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="167"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4565" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f prime (k  _{S} ^{*} )= theta </SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 를 만족시키는 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714849" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="168"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2270" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>k  _{S} ^{*} (t)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 이었다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><CHAR>본 Ramsey모형은 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714850" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="169"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6165" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f prime (k*)= theta +r</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 를 만족시키는 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714851" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="170"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2315" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>k*(t)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>가 최적경제성장경로가 된다. 이자율 r의 추가로 최적경제성장경로가 줄어드는데(</CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714852" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="174"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5905" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>k*(t)&lt;k  _{S} ^{*} (t)</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>) 이를 ‘수정된 황금률성장경로’라 한다.</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="5" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="33"><AUTONUM Number="38" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 두당자본과 두당소비가 상수이므로 총소비, 총자본, 총생산이 모두 노동증가율 n으로 똑같이 증가하므로 ‘</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="22"><CHAR>균형성장경로(balanced growth path)</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="33"><CHAR>’라고도 함</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><CHAR>(그림)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"/></P><P ParaShape="25" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="30"><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714853" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="162"><SIZE Height="2250" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="11365" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>c'(t)=- {U prime (f prime -( theta +r))} over {U '' }</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 에서 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2110714854" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="164"><SIZE Height="2250" HeightRelTo="Absolute" 